def get_final_ucb_features(xml_file):
    
    df = pd.read_excel(xml_file, sheet_name='final')
    finalUcbPeptides = df['Peptide']

    ucbPeptide2Feature = dataSet.feature_table.copy()
    ucbPeptide2Feature['UCB_PEPTIDE'] = dataSet.feature_table['sequence'].str.replace(r'\([\d.]+\)', '*')
    final_ucb_features = ucbPeptide2Feature[ucbPeptide2Feature['UCB_PEPTIDE'].isin(finalUcbPeptides)]['FEATURE']
    return final_ucb_features

data = {}
data['Nimbolide'] = {'file_path':'{}/ucb/nimbolide/peptideList.csv'.format(resource_dir), 
                     'expected_hits' : ['RNF114_C8'], 
                     'peptides_to_hits' : {'DC*GGAAQLAGPAAEADPLGR': 'RNF114 C8'},
                     'xml_file':'{}/ucb/nimbolide/081018 nimbolide in situ isoTOP 231.xlsx'.format(resource_dir), 
                     'feature_type':FeatureType.GENE_PROBE_LOC}

data['EN6'] = {'file_path':'{}/ucb/en6/peptideList.csv'.format(resource_dir), 
               'expected_hits' : ['Atp6v1a_C277'],
               'peptides_to_hits' : {'YSNSDVIIYVGC*GER': 'Atp6v1a C277'},
               'xml_file':'{}/ucb/en6/031718 EN6 MEF isoTOP_with filtering+qualityv2.xlsx'.format(resource_dir), 
               'feature_type':FeatureType.GENE_PROBE_LOC}


for data_name in data.keys():
    file_path = data[data_name]['file_path']
    feature_type = data[data_name]['feature_type']
    dataSet = transformer.transform(resource=file_path,
                                    transform_function=peplisttransformer.transform_peptidelist,
                                    featureType=feature_type,
                                    test_quant_channel='HEAVY',
                                    control_quant_channel='LIGHT')
    
    dataSet = contrast.build_contrast_data(dataSet)
    data[data_name]['dataSet'] = dataSet
    data[data_name]['final_ucb_features'] = get_final_ucb_features(data[data_name]['xml_file'])
    dataSet.ucbPrePeakQualFilter = pd.read_excel(data[data_name]['xml_file'], sheet_name='peak quality') 
    dataSet.ucbFinal = pd.read_excel(data[data_name]['xml_file'], sheet_name='final')

sns.set(rc={'figure.figsize':(10,5)})
sns.set_style("white")
sns.set_context("paper", font_scale=0.8)
sns.set_context("talk", font_scale=0.8)
#

def label_point(point, x=None, y=None, ax=None):
    bbox = {'fc': '0.8', 'pad': 0}
    props = {'ha': 'center', 'va': 'center', 'bbox': None}
    label = point['FEATURE'].split(',')[0]
    
    ax.text(point[x]+.04, point[y], label, props, rotation=-35, fontsize=12)

def get_hue(feature, expected_hits=None, hit_features=None, contrast_table=None, show_filtered=False):
    finalUcbFeature = contrast_table[contrast_table['FEATURE'] == feature]['IS_FINAL_UCB_FEATURE'].values[0]
    
    if feature in hit_features.values:
        return 'Hit'
    elif feature in expected_hits:
        return 'Expected hit'
    elif (not finalUcbFeature) & show_filtered:
        return 'UCB FILTER'    
    else:
        return ''
    

def do_scatter(contrast_table, px=None, py=None, datasetName=None, xcut=None, ycut=None, 
               expected_hits=None, show_filtered=False, label_all_hits=False, project_results_dir=None):
    
    pallet = sns.color_palette("hls", 3)   
    legend_loc = 'upper left'
    legend_pos = (-10, 0)

    hue = None
    hits = pd.DataFrame(columns=contrast_table.columns)
    if xcut and ycut:
        hits = contrast_table[((contrast_table[px] > xcut) & (contrast_table[py] > ycut))]
        
    hue = contrast_table['FEATURE'].apply(get_hue, 
                                      expected_hits=expected_hits, 
                                      hit_features=hits['FEATURE'], 
                                      contrast_table=contrast_table, 
                                      show_filtered=show_filtered)
    
    ax = sns.scatterplot(x=px, y=py, data=contrast_table, 
                         hue=hue)
    
    sns.despine()
    
    ## Lable features
    hits = contrast_table[contrast_table['FEATURE'].isin(expected_hits)]

    if label_all_hits:
        exp_hits = contrast_table[(contrast_table[px] >= xcut) & (contrast_table[py] >= ycut)]
        label_features = pd.concat([hits['FEATURE'], exp_hits['FEATURE']])
        hits = contrast_table[contrast_table['FEATURE'].isin(label_features)]
    hits.apply(label_point, axis=1, x=px, y=py, ax=ax)
    
    
    if xcut and ycut:
        title = '{} n={}\nhits={}>{}, {}>{}\n\n'.format(datasetName, contrast_table.index.size, px, xcut, py, ycut)
    else:
        title = '{} n={}'.format(datasetName, contrast_table.index.size)
    ax.set_title(title)
    #ax.legend(loc=legend_loc, bbox_to_anchor=(0, 0.9))
    
    showfilter_tag = 'show-ucb-filter' if show_filtered else ''
    plt.savefig('{}/{}-x{}-y{}{}.png'.format(project_results_dir,
                                             datasetName, px, py, showfilter_tag), bbox_inches='tight')
    
    plt.figure()
    
def do_violin(df, column=None, dataset_name=None, png_name=None):
    ax = sns.violinplot(df[column])
    median = np.median(df[column])
    dev = np.std(df[column])
    kurtosis = stats.kurtosis(df[column])
    ax.set_title('{} {} \nmedian={:.2f}, stddev={:.2f}, kurtosis={:.2f}'.format(dataset_name, column, median, dev, kurtosis))
    
    plt.savefig('{}/{}-{}.png'.format(project_results_dir,
                                             dataset_name, png_name), bbox_inches='tight')
    plt.figure()
    
    
def do_ratio_plot(ucbDF, title=None, px=None, py=None, png_name=None, hue=None, 
                 peptides_to_hits=None, project_results_dir=None):
    
    ax = sns.scatterplot(x=px, y=py, 
                         data=ucbDF, 
                         hue=hue)
    
    ax.set_title('isoTOP-ABPP analysis of {}, n={}'.format(title, ucbDF.index.size))
    
    
    
    if peptides_to_hits:
        hits = ucbDF[ucbDF['Peptide'].isin(peptides_to_hits.keys())]
        hits['FEATURE'] = hits['Peptide'].map(peptides_to_hits)
        hits.apply(label_point, axis=1, x=px, y=py, ax=ax)
        
    plt.savefig('{}/{}'.format(project_results_dir, png_name))
    
    plt.figure()
    
    
def do_barplot(dataSet, title=None, features=None, project_results_dir=None, is_psm=False):
    if is_psm:
        df = dataSet.psm_obs_table
    else:
        df = dataSet.obs_table

    for feature in features:
        df = df[df['FEATURE'] == feature]
        
        fold_change_col = 'fold_change_psm' if is_psm else 'fold_change'
        p_value = 'p.value_psm' if is_psm else 'p.value'
        
        featureDataDF = dataSet.contrast_table[dataSet.contrast_table['FEATURE'] == feature]
        average_ratio = featureDataDF[fold_change_col].values[0]
        p_value = featureDataDF[p_value].values[0]
        
        
        """df = df.assign(ABUNDANCE= df['ABUNDANCE'].apply(lambda x : x[0]))
        df['PSM_SAMPLE'] = df.groupby(['SAMPLE']).cumcount()+1
        df['PSM_NUM'] = df['PSM_SAMPLE'].astype(str)
        df['PSM_PAIR'] = df['PAIR'] + '_PSM' + df['PSM_NUM']
"""
        ax=sns.barplot(x='PAIR', y='ABUNDANCE', data=df, hue='QUANT_CHANNEL', order=None)
        
        for item in ax.get_xticklabels():
            item.set_rotation(90)
        
        ax.set_title('{} {} (average_ratio={:.2f}, p.value={:.4f})'.format(title, feature, average_ratio, p_value))
        plt.legend(bbox_to_anchor=(1.05, 1), loc=2, borderaxespad=0.)

        png_name = '{}_{}.png'.format(dataset_name, feature)
        plt.savefig('{}/{}_{}'.format(project_results_dir, feature, png_name), bbox_inches='tight')

        plt.figure()

def do_plots(dataSet=None, dataset_name=None, 
             expected_hits=None, 
             final_ucb_features=None, 
             peptides_to_hits=None):
    
    df = dataSet.ucbPrePeakQualFilter
    df['probe-modified peptides'] = df['average area ratio'].rank()
    df['control (light) vs.\n treated (heavy) ratio'] = df['average area ratio']
    df['log2(control (light) vs.\n treated (heavy) ratio)'] = df['average area ratio'].apply(np.log2)
    finalDF = dataSet.ucbFinal
    df['Final Feature'] = df['Peptide'].isin(finalDF['Peptide'])
    
    finalDF['probe-modified peptides'] = finalDF['average area ratio'].rank()
    finalDF['control (light) vs.\n treated (heavy) ratio'] = finalDF['average area ratio']
    finalDF['log2(control (light) vs.\n treated (heavy) ratio)'] = finalDF['average area ratio'].apply(np.log2)
    

    if dataset_name == 'Nimbolide':
        title='{} \n(>4 for >4, >3 for >3)'.format(dataset_name)
    elif dataset_name == 'EN6':
        title='{} \n(filtering for 3 out of 3 >4)'.format(dataset_name)
        
    do_ratio_plot(df, title=title, hue=None,
                  px='probe-modified peptides', 
                  py='control (light) vs.\n treated (heavy) ratio', 
                  png_name='{}_prefiltered_rscores'.format(dataset_name), 
                  project_results_dir=project_results_dir)
    
    do_ratio_plot(df, title=title, hue=None,
                  px='probe-modified peptides', 
                  py='log2(control (light) vs.\n treated (heavy) ratio)',
                  png_name='{}_log2_prefiltered_rscores'.format(dataset_name), 
                  project_results_dir=project_results_dir)
    
    do_violin(df, column='log2(control (light) vs.\n treated (heavy) ratio)', png_name='area_ratio',
              dataset_name=dataset_name)
    
    do_ratio_plot(df, title=title, hue='Final Feature',
                  px='probe-modified peptides', 
                  py='log2(control (light) vs.\n treated (heavy) ratio)', 
                  png_name='{}_log2_hued_prefiltered_rscores'.format(dataset_name), 
                  project_results_dir=project_results_dir)
    
    title='{} \n(Final)'.format(dataset_name)
    do_ratio_plot(finalDF, title=title, hue=None,
                  px='probe-modified peptides', 
                  py='control (light) vs.\n treated (heavy) ratio', 
                  peptides_to_hits=peptides_to_hits, 
                  png_name='{}_final_rscores'.format(dataset_name), 
                  project_results_dir=project_results_dir)
    
    do_ratio_plot(finalDF, title=title, hue=None,
                  px='probe-modified peptides', 
                  py='log2(control (light) vs.\n treated (heavy) ratio)', 
                  peptides_to_hits=peptides_to_hits, 
                  png_name='{}_log2_final_rscores'.format(dataset_name), 
                  project_results_dir=project_results_dir)
    
    do_barplot(dataSet, features=expected_hits, 
                     project_results_dir=project_results_dir, 
                     title=dataset_name, 
                     is_psm=True)
    
    title = 'isoTOP-ABPP analysis of {}'.format(dataset_name)

    dataSet.contrast_table['IS_FINAL_UCB_FEATURE'] = dataSet.contrast_table['FEATURE'].isin(final_ucb_features)
    
    do_scatter(dataSet.contrast_table, px='log2(Fold Change)', py='-log10(FDR)', 
           datasetName=title, xcut=1, ycut=1, expected_hits=expected_hits, 
           show_filtered=False, project_results_dir=project_results_dir)
    
    do_scatter(dataSet.contrast_table, px='log2(Fold Change)_psm', py='-log10(FDR)_psm', 
           datasetName=title, xcut=2, ycut=2, expected_hits=expected_hits, 
           show_filtered=False, project_results_dir=project_results_dir)
    
    do_barplot(dataSet=dataSet, features=expected_hits, title=dataset_name, 
                project_results_dir=project_results_dir)
